    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't feel like a \"phase\" though. it feels more permanent than that. like the well has finally run dry and there's nothing underneath it. i look at all these half-finished pieces and i just feel like a fraud. why keep pretending there's still something to find when everything just feels so hollow and meaningless?",
